I often stay at Hilton properties and the Toronto Hilton Garden Inn offers a great, and expected, level of service and comfort.	The pool and spa were much appreciated as was the Marquis dining room where we had a great breakfast in a relaxed atmosphere.	The room was a fairly typical Hilton Garden Inn room, which I like, with great & free high speed access, a fridge that came in very handy and a solid shower and bed.	My girlfriend and I stayed at the Hilton Garden Inn over the July-August long weekend and had a great time!	The Hilton Garden Inn is a good choice for either business or leisure in Toronto.